## 7. File Budget (13 files)

```
demo-src/
  vite.config.js                  (1) configure base + outDir
  index.html                      (2) Google Fonts link, mount point
  src/
    main.jsx                      (3) Vite entry
    App.jsx                       (4) root state, layout, view routing
    data/
      properties.js               (5) 25 properties, Unsplash image URLs
    styles/
      tokens.css                  (6) CSS custom properties, typography base, utilities
    components/
      Navbar.jsx                  (7) wordmark, nav links, favorites badge, mobile menu
      FilterPanel.jsx             (8) search, price, type, beds, status, sort controls
      PropertyList.jsx            (9) list of cards, scroll sync, map highlight
      MapView.jsx                 (10) Leaflet init, price pins, flyTo, pin/list sync
      PropertyDetail.jsx          (11) modal: gallery carousel, specs, description, inquiry form, favorites toggle
      FavoritesView.jsx           (12) saved properties grid, empty state

michaelwegter.com/
  src/data/workSamples.js         (13) append new entry
```

Total: 13 files. 1 over ~12 cap; justified by 10/10 richness mandate.

